    {
      "id": "detail-be",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 365,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 210,
      "text": "BACKEND — Détail par couche :\n\n🟢 Unit (mock repo) :\n• Use cases: CreateTemplateUseCase, etc.\n• Entités domain: validation, logique\n• Exceptions: TemplateNotFoundError\n\n🟠 Integration (testcontainers) :\n• Repository + vraie BDD PostgreSQL\n• Endpoints + httpx AsyncClient\n• Migrations Alembic up/down\n\n🔴 E2E (tous services réels) :\n• Flow complet: créer → lister → modifier → supprimer\n• Docker Compose + testcontainers",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 315,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 315,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "detail-fe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 365,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 210,
      "text": "FRONTEND — Détail par couche :\n\n🟢 Unit (vitest) :\n• Components: TemplateCard, VersionBadge\n• Hooks: useTemplates (React Query mocké)\n• Mappers: DTO → Model conversion\n• Services: catalogApi (axios mocké)\n\n🟠 Integration (vitest + MSW) :\n• Pages complètes: CatalogPage, DetailPage\n• MSW intercepte les appels API\n• Vérifie le rendu avec données réelles\n\n🔴 E2E (Playwright) :\n• Naviguer → filtrer → voir détail → déployer\n• Vrai navigateur + vraie API",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 316,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 316,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "coverage",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "COUVERTURE CIBLE :\n80% global minimum — 90% sur la logique métier\n(use cases backend + hooks/mappers frontend)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
